summary: The lab aims to describe the setup and equipment available in the wet lab space for eye-related experiments.

procedure.step: Prepare fixative for the anterior capsule to reduce elasticity.
Prepare fixatives for injection into limbs to induce cataracts.
Use the microwave to induce a cataract in a large eye.
Store the large eye in the mini fridge.
Use the operating microscope with the teaching scope for instruction and observation.
Arrange all the instruments on the work table.
Secure the pig eye on a foam head using pins.
